      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/46/940",
      "text": [
        " اَلصَّلاَةِ اَلْمَفْرُوضَةِ حَتَّى يَبْكِيَ فَقَالَ «قُرَّةُ عَيْنٍ وَ اَللَّهِ» وَقَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ «إِذَا كَانَ ذَلِكَ فَاذْكُرْنِي عِنْدَهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.940 - Mansur ibn Yunus Buzurj asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a person who strives to cry during the obligatory prayer until tears flow.\nImam (as) replied: \"It is a source of great joy, by Allah (swt).\"\nThe Imam also said: \"When this happens, remember me in that moment”."
        ]
      }
    },
